text: Tokelo Moyakhe (born 3 August 1993), is a South African rapper and songwriter popularly known as Maglera Doe Boy (or simply Maglera). He became famous after the release of "Never Ride" by MashBeatz after the single went viral on video sharing platform TikTok. == Discography == === Studio albums === * Diaspora (2022) === Collaborative albums === * Champion Music () (2020) * Champion Music 2 () (2022) === Extended plays === * Progression (2015) == Awards and nominations == Year Award ceremony Category Recipient/Nominated work Results 2022 11th South African Hip Hop Awards Best remix "Never Ride Remix" == References == == Other websites == * Category:1993 births Category:Living people
